steps.name: Given I am login on staging env by created timestamp project
When I navigate to menu "Web editor" with submenu "Web editor"
Then I should see Web Editor screen display
When I select tab list with name "Pages"
When I select tab name Pages with index 1
When I add new page in web editor with name "JIT001bWebPage" & slug "/JIT001bWebPage"
When I add new page in web editor with name "duplicatedJIT001bWebPage" & slug "/duplicatedJIT001bWebPage"
Then I should see the page in web editor with name "JIT001bWebPage" & slug "/JIT001bWebPage" display in list "Pages"
Then I should see the page in web editor with name "duplicatedJIT001bWebPage" & slug "/duplicatedJIT001bWebPage" display in list "Pages"
When I rename page in web editor name from "JIT001bWebPage" to "invalid<>?@#$updateJIT001bWebPage" & slug "empty"
